11 An act relating to the study and design of a long-term care trust fund
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 Sec. 1. LONG-TERM CARE TRUST FUND; AGENCY OF
14 ADMINISTRATION; STUDY; REPORT
15 (a) The Secretary of Administration shall study and design a trust fund
16 that would provide for long-term care of eligible persons. In particular, the
17 Secretary shall study the following:
18 (1) the creation and design of the trust fund based on a social insurance
19 model, such as Social Security;
20 (2) a funding plan addressing:
